          Dec 18, 2013           - Thomson Reuters ONE      






Brussels, December 18, 2013 - RHJ International ("RHJI", "the Company") is announcing today that it has sold its remaining 10.9% stake in business consulting services company SigmaXYZ through an initial public offering ("IPO") on the Tokyo Stock Exchange ("TSE"). The IPO of RHJI's stake, equating to 490,500 shares in the newly-listed entity, follows the earlier sale of a 10.9% stake to a number of Japanese buyers in September 2013 and has generated proceeds of EUR9.6 million (JPY1,358 million),  




